{"tid":2080564,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"標普確認香港AA+信用評級　港版國安法不影響經濟","createTime":"2020-06-26T13:39:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T05:57:50.000Z","uid":225931,"like":7,"dislike":154,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"6833976e702256ac3bab1ca802c543406fd36449","tid":2080564,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T13:39:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200521/340171049083736064.jpeg/vSgQnjQSuEUtj65FsFTtpD-gupsv8clhfEtLcnxLS3I?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200521%2F340171049083736064.jpeg%2FvSgQnjQSuEUtj65FsFTtpD-gupsv8clhfEtLcnxLS3I%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=e4773894&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國際評級機構標普發表報告，今年本港經濟或會再次出現嚴重收縮，政府推出財政刺激措施導致赤字擴大，惟目前的財政緩衝足以吸收有關措施對信貸的影響。該投資評級機構確認予香港政府長期發行人「AA+」信用評級，及短期發行人「A+」信用評級。<br />\n<br />\n標普指出前景展望維持「穩定」，主要因為香港強勁的經濟及金融指標仍有利於鞏固政府信譽，足以抵禦長期社會緊張局勢，及未來一至兩年內疫情影響。<br />\n<br />\n此外標普認為即將實施「港區國安法」而導致制度改變，不會影響香港根據《基本法》制定經濟政策的自主權，同時美國與香港之間貿易關係亦不會發生任何變化，且不會香港的金融業發展及經濟增長造成嚴重損害。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/491010/%E6%A8%99%E6%99%AE%E7%A2%BA%E8%AA%8D%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AFaa-%E4%BF%A1%E7%94%A8%E8%A9%95%E7%B4%9A-%E6%B8%AF%E7%89%88%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E4%B8%8D%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E8%25A8%258A%2F491010%2F%25E6%25A8%2599%25E6%2599%25AE%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25AA%258D%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AFaa-%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E7%2594%25A8%25E8%25A9%2595%25E7%25B4%259A-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%2589%2588%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E9%259F%25BF%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F&d=jQldmXM9xAXOA%2BwUl6G2h9%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=c4d4f651\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/491010/%E6%A8%99%E6%99%AE%E7%A2%BA%E8%AA%8D%E9%A6