faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff89626f16c723331dc6893114be32cd1d5821ea","tid":2080564,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T06:31:13.000Z","msg":"D評級機構<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一向都係參考<br />\n係咁勁嘅07/08年金融海嘯個期做過乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8702daeb30185ad525e329d911fd299ab6312a1","tid":2080564,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T06:38:55.000Z","msg":"其實d評級機構真係9up多<br />\n求其search下past history佢地準確程度<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.fool.com/amp/investing/general/2012/03/14/ratings-agencies-are-always-the-last-to-know.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.fool.com%2Famp%2Finvesting%2Fgeneral%2F2012%2F03%2F14%2Fratings-agencies-are-always-the-last-to-know.aspx&d=jQldmXM9xAXOA%2BwUl6G2h9%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=7cefe963\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.fool.com/amp/investing/general/2012/03/14/ratings-agencies-are-always-the-last-to-know.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>Ratings Agencies Are Always the Last to Know<br />\n<br />\n...Moody's put Lehman Brothers' investment-grade A2 rating &quot;on review&quot; a mere five days before it filed for bankruptcy. Standard &amp; Poor's gave American International Group (NYSE: AIG) an investment-grade A rating less than a week before the insurance company was nationalized. Merrill Lynch and Bear Stearns sported investment-grade ratings when they were rescued by Bank of America (NYSE: BAC) and JPMorgan Chase (NYSE: JPM), respectively. And both Fannie Mae and Freddie Mac had highly coveted AAA ratings at the time they were forced into conservatorship.<br />\n<br />\nMore recently, all three of the ratings agencies effectively missed the impending collapse of derivatives broker MF Global, which we covered extensively in our award-winning series, &quot;The Astonishing Collapse of MF Global.&quot; Moody's and Fitch didn't remove the company's investment-grade rating until a measly six days before it filed for bankruptcy protection. And Standard &amp; Poor's waited until the day of MF Global's filing to downgrade the then-defunct broker...</blockquote>"},{"pid":"58df768d6f71566e8b9b7aee895a018c7668525e","tid":2080564,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35152bb577bf06b9a004b402da98fffc1da42855","tid":2080564,"uid":225931,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T18:44:52.000Z","msg":"連登又燈中"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T06:41:28.000Z","msg":"標普講一句你就信足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cc45d6454b69cead534e77a1d4abe4d43132f21","tid":2080564,"uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T06:41:48.000Z","msg":"再次證明連登高估國際反應<br />\n根本香港就係比全世界食大茶飯<br />\n有錢搵理閪得你過咩法<br />\n反正唔拉班做生意既鬼佬咪得"},{"pid":"ce8f109ad87c8a644dfdb8e70fc502d32ce62d7f","tid":2080564,"uid":316927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T08:11:42.000Z","msg":"DLLM poor"},{"pid":"750b1b1d5c87e6943790b18a04374753d485ac0f","tid":2080564,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6428d3637c38fe2bc34229d603f61d5c108d748e","tid":2080564,"uid":199957,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"35152bb577bf06b9a004b402da98fffc1da42855","tid":2080564,"uid":225931,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T18:44:52.000Z","msg":"連登又燈中"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T18:53:46.000Z","msg":"西方唔做野又真係冇計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地唔做野=自炒<br />\n<br />\n大佬當年孫中山如果係今日既局面都玩唔到落去啦 <br />\n想召集人俾武器[我地希望你和大清保持和平 大家理性溝通]<br />\n想外國介入[我地精神上永遠同孫中山你企係同一陣線]<br />\n<br />\n屌你老味呀 你玩埋佢啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T10:25:31.000Z","msg":"真係